****PERMISSION****

chmod 751 folder (only folder) ex: op/rwxr-x--x
chmod 777 file1 file2 (multiple)
chmod 644 * (all files)
chmod 555 folder1 -r (it will chanage both folder & files)
chmod 777 folder/* (It will only apply the insider folder data not applicable the folder)

r = read = 4
w = write = 2
x = executive = 1
- = nothing =0

ex: rw-r--r-- = 4+2+0 ; 4+0+0 ; 4+0+0  = 644
    rwxr-x--x = 4+2+1 ; 4+0+1 ; 0+0+1  = 751

